    "In addition, we also noticed that some studies have pointed out that LLM can also be used in network security education [47]- [49], which is also an application of LLM in defending against reconnaissance attacks.",
    "The Defensive Role of LLM in the Foothold Establishment PhaseVulnerability attacks are the most dominant methods of attack in the foothold phase, where an attacker will use specific vulnerabilities to successfully hack into a system and establish a foothold at the edge of the network to carry out subsequent attacks [50].",
